info.description:
Introduction
============

This is a facet navigation portlet. The goal is to create a simple implementation that can be extended,
rather than a package that does everything.

Change history
==============

0.1a - (2009-11-25)
-------------------

* Initial alpha release

Contributors
============

* Robin Harms Oredsson (author)
* Martin Lundwall (co-author)
* Raphael Ritz (Lots of good ideas)
* Joergen Modin (Keeping us on track :)

Known Issues
============

* None that we know of
